Deployment scripting tool

Description

./rpms/configure-storagegrid.py

A Python script used to automate the configuration of a StorageGRID system.

./rpms/configure-sga.py

A Python script used to automate the configuration of StorageGRID appliances. ./rpms/configure-storagegrid.sample.json An example configuration file for use with the

configure-storagegrid.py script.

